_sText:
EDIT: modified the RAR file so its easier for beginners to know where to put the map file.

(Yes, I know, I'm somehow missing textures for "Reflect All".)

Ok this is my VERY FIRST MAP that I worked on greatly. I made it in THREE DAYS... on the weekend.
First map I've ever released that I am proud of.


This is De_StoneDust.

STORY:

In an abandoned area in Africa, there resides a small computer which stores information about some rocket.
The terrorists must destroy that machine, OR the major supplies to make the machine which holds info and processes which can make a deadly rocket.
The Counter-terrorists are protecting the rocket info because of the orders from the US government.... whatever their idea was to protect the bomb.

So yeah.

Another Dust map, and I should say it's fun.
HAVE FUN!
